lead_paragraph: The last time the Cleveland Indians won the World Series, Dewey led Truman in the polls. The Chicago Cubs' last title was 13 days after the first Ford Model T car was completed.

headline.print_headline: Next Year Here: Lovable Losers Cubs, Indians Meet in Series
